description: Muscle studs Cameron Adams and Phenix Saint battle it out with Blake Daniels and DJ in a testosterone fueled tag team match in front of a live audience. Four hot muscle studs all with awesome wrestling skills and big, meaty cocks fight it out for the right to dominate, humiliate and fuck the losers in front of a screaming crowd of their fans. Remember, anything can happen since this is a Live match and, when it does, sexy stud Troy Daniels is thrown into the mix. Who will survive and come out on top and who will be on the bottom and surrender their hole to be pounded into oblivion? This is one NK match that will have you sitting on the edge of your seat.
title: Cameron Adams and Phenix Saint vs Blake Daniels and DJ
